Bandits on Friday morning kidnapped unspecified number of students of the Government Girls Secondary School at Tatafa Local Government Area of Zamfara State. The school was invaded in the early hours of Friday as students were preparing for their classes in the school.
The mass kidnapping of the students is coming at a time the Zamfara State governor is celebrating repentant bandits and disbursing money in millions to claimed repentant bandits. The number of students kidnapped by the bandits is yet to be ascertained.
Details of the Friday kidnapping later.





